# Input file for Felix version :main: :15 December 2025:
# ------------------------------------
Scatter factor method:
    Kirkland, 0
    Lobato, 1
    Peng, 2
    Doyle-Turner, 3
    Kappa (Coppens relativisitic RHF), 4   ***up to atomic number Z=54
    Kappa (Bunge non-relativisitic RHF), 5

Absorption:
    None, 0
    Proportional, 1 (value given by absorption_per)
    Bird & King (Thomas parameterisation), 2

Refine modes:
    Simulation only, S
    Structure Factors, A  ***not yet re-implemented
    Atomic Coordinates, B  ***partially implemented
    Occupancies, C
    Isotropic atomic displacement parameters, D
    Anisotropic atomic displacement parameters, E
    Lattice Parameters, F  ***partially implemented
    Lattice Angles, G  ***not yet implemented
    Convergence Angle, H
    Accelerating Voltage, I  ***not yet implemented
    Kappa, J  ***partially implemented up to atomic number Z=54
    Proportion of valence electrons, K  ***partially implemented up to atomic number Z=54
	Optimisation of beam pool, O

Refinements B, C, D, E, J, K are applied to the atom(s) in cif given by atomic_sites
Refinement scale gives initial change in the refined parameter
This is fractional atomic coordinate for position refinement, fraction for everything else i.e. 0.01 is 1 percent

Refine method:
	One parameter at a time, gradient descent, parabolic, 0
	Multiparameter, vector gradient descent, parabolic, 1

Correlation type:
    Phase (Fourier), 0
    Pearson (zncc), 1
    Pearson (zncc) with sub-pixel alignment, 2
    Pearson (zncc) with affine transform, 3
    Pearson (zncc) with Sobel filter, 4

Image processing:
    None, 0
    Gaussian blur, 1, given by blur radius
    Fitted gaussian blur 2, that which gives the best figure of merit

Plot:
    None, 0
    Unit Cell, beam pool, montages, figure of merit, 1
    As (1) + thickness plot, blur fit 2
    As (2) + difference plots, 3

Write flag:
    Basic print output, 0
    More detailed output, 1

Debug_ flag:
    No output, 0
    Lots of output, 1  *** could be merged with write flag and could add more levels
# ------------------------------------

# Control flags
write_flag                = 0
scatter_factor_method     = 4
holz_flag                 = 0
absorption_method         = 2
byte_size                 = 2

# Isotropic (0) Anisotropic (1)
Debye_model               = 0     

# Beam selection criteria
min_reflection_pool       = 100
min_strong_beams          = 20
min_weak_beams            = 0
g_limit                   = 0.0

# Crystal settings
incident_beam_direction   = [1, -1, 0]
x_direction               = [0, 0, -1]
normal                    = [1, -1, 0]
initial_thickness         = 1480.0
final_thickness           = 1481.0
delta_thickness           = 20.0
debye_waller_constant     = 0.0
absorption_per            = 10.0

# Microscope settings
convergence_angle         = 0.661
accelerating_voltage_kv   = 200.0
acceptance_angle          = 0.0

# Output options
image_radius              = 76
plot                      = 2
image_processing          = 1
blur_radius               = 1.0
print_flag                = 0
debug                     = 0

# Refinement specific flags
refine_mode               = 'J'
refine_method             = 0
refinement_scale          = 0.2
correlation_type          = 2
atomic_sites              = [0]
exit_criteria             = 0.00005
precision                 = 0.00002
weighting_flag            = 0
no_of_ugs                 = 40